ies using benefits, life insurance, and exit planning that work together to protect today and prepare for tomorrow. </p><ul><li>60 Minutes</li><li><span>Standard Webinar Price: $49.00</span></li><li><span>CEU Unlimited Subscriber Price: Included in your subscription.</span></li></ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__footer\">\n<a class=\"btn btn--secondary\" href=\"/ceu/webinars/small-business-planning-3d-benefits-protection-exit-strategies-20260428\">Learn More and Register<span class=\"u-sr-only\">for\n\t\t\t\t\tSmall Business Planning in 3D:  Benefits, Protection &amp; Exit Strategies</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div>\n<div class=\"views-row\">\n<article class=\"u-margin-lg-bottom u-box-shadow ceu-webinar-list__webinar\">\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__image\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2023-05/Auto_PredictiveAI.jpg%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__content\">\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__eyebrow\">\n<span class=\"u-text-uppercase badge badge--dark ceu-webinar-list__webinar__eyebrow__badge\">\n\t\t\t\tApr. 28 2026 01:00 PM EDT\n\t\t\t</span>\n</div>\n<h2 class=\"h4 u-margin-hug ceu-webinar-list__webinar__heading\">\n<a href=\"/ceu/webinars/powering-protection-electric-hybrid-vehicles-impact-insurance-20260428\">\n\t\t\t\tPowering Up Protection: Electric &amp; Hybrid Vehicles' Impact on Insurance\n\t\t\t</a>\n</h2>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__body\">\n<p>EVs are changing everything from batteries to collision repair. Join us to explore the risks and solutions shaping the future of auto insurance.</p><ul><li>60 Minutes</li><li><span>Standard Webinar Price: $49.00</span></li><li><span>CEU Unlimited Subscriber Price: Included in your subscription.</span></li></ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__footer\">\n<a class=\"btn btn--secondary\" href=\"/ceu/webinars/powering-protection-electric-hybrid-vehicles-impact-insurance-20260428\">Learn More and Register<span class=\"u-sr-only\">for\n\t\t\t\t\tPowering Up Protection: Electric &amp; Hybrid Vehicles' Impact on Insurance</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div>\n<div class=\"views-row\">\n<article class=\"u-margin-lg-bottom u-box-shadow ceu-webinar-list__webinar\">\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__image\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2024-07/Highway_Flooding.webp%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__content\">\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__eyebrow\">\n<span class=\"u-text-uppercase badge badge--dark ceu-webinar-list__webinar__eyebrow__badge\">\n\t\t\t\tApr. 29 2026 11:00 AM EDT\n\t\t\t</span>\n</div>\n<h2 class=\"h4 u-margin-hug ceu-webinar-list__webinar__heading\">\n<a href=\"/ceu/webinars/floods-faults-firestorms-wildfire-earthquake-and-flood-risk-us-20260429\">\n\t\t\t\tFloods, Faults &amp; Firestorms: Wildfire, Earthquake and Flood Risk in the US\n\t\t\t</a>\n</h2>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__body\">\n<p>Wildfires, earthquakes, and floods aren’t just regional concerns. Discover how these threats are growing nationwide—and what insurance professionals need to know to stay ahead.</p><ul><li>60 Minutes</li><li><span>Standard Webinar Price: $49.00</span></li><li><span>CEU Unlimited Subscriber Price: Included in your subscription.</span></li></ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__footer\">\n<a class=\"btn btn--secondary\" href=\"/ceu/webinars/floods-faults-firestorms-wildfire-earthquake-and-flood-risk-us-20260429\">Learn More and Register<span class=\"u-sr-only\">for\n\t\t\t\t\tFloods, Faults &amp; Firestorms: Wildfire, Earthquake and Flood Risk in the US</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div>\n<div class=\"views-row\">\n<article class=\"u-margin-lg-bottom u-box-shadow ceu-webinar-list__webinar\">\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__image\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2025-07/Webinar-Insured-Endorsements-600x450.webp%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__content\">\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__eyebrow\">\n<span class=\"u-text-uppercase badge badge--dark ceu-webinar-list__webinar__eyebrow__badge\">\n\t\t\t\tApr. 29 2026 01:00 PM EDT\n\t\t\t</span>\n</div>\n<h2 class=\"h4 u-margin-hug ceu-webinar-list__webinar__heading\">\n<a href=\"/ceu/webinars/whos-covered-demystifying-additional-insured-endorsements-20260429\">\n\t\t\t\tWho's Covered? Demystifying Additional Insured Endorsements\n\t\t\t</a>\n</h2>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__body\">\n<p>When does adding an additional insured make strategic sense, and when does it create more risk than reward? Demystify these endorsements, from compliance requirements to contractual landmines. Walk away ready to protect your clients and avoid costly missteps. </p><ul><li>60 Minutes</li><li><span>Standard Webinar Price: $49.00</span></li><li><span>CEU Unlimited Subscriber Price: Included in your subscription.</span></li></ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__footer\">\n<a class=\"btn btn--secondary\" href=\"/ceu/webinars/whos-covered-demystifying-additional-insured-endorsements-20260429\">Learn More and Register<span class=\"u-sr-only\">for\n\t\t\t\t\tWho's Covered? Demystifying Additional Insured Endorsements</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div>\n<div class=\"views-row\">\n<article class=\"u-margin-lg-bottom u-box-shadow ceu-webinar-list__webinar\">\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__image\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2026-03/webinar-new-age-insurance-pricing-600x336.jpg%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__content\">\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__eyebrow\">\n<span class=\"u-text-uppercase badge badge--dark ceu-webinar-list__webinar__eyebrow__badge\">\n\t\t\t\tApr. 30 2026 11:00 AM EDT\n\t\t\t</span>\n</div>\n<h2 class=\"h4 u-margin-hug ceu-webinar-list__webinar__heading\">\n<a href=\"/ceu/webinars/personalized-or-problematic-exploring-new-age-insurance-pricing-20260430\">\n\t\t\t\tPersonalized or Problematic: Exploring the New Age of Insurance Pricing\n\t\t\t</a>\n</h2>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__body\">\n<p>Examine how tech-fueled personalization in insurance pricing challenges long-held ideas of fairness, transparency, and public trust—and what it means for the future of coverage. </p><ul><li>120 Minutes</li><li><span>Standard Webinar Price: $64.00</span></li><li><span>CEU Unlimited Subscriber Price: Included in your subscription.</span></li></ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__footer\">\n<a class=\"btn btn--secondary\" href=\"/ceu/webinars/personalized-or-problematic-exploring-new-age-insurance-pricing-20260430\">Learn More and Register<span class=\"u-sr-only\">for\n\t\t\t\t\tPersonalized or Problematic: Exploring the New Age of Insurance Pricing</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div>\n<div class=\"views-row\">\n<article class=\"u-margin-lg-bottom u-box-shadow ceu-webinar-list__webinar\">\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__image\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2026-02/webinar-backyard-600x450.jpg%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__content\">\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__eyebrow\">\n<span class=\"u-text-uppercase badge badge--dark ceu-webinar-list__webinar__eyebrow__badge\">\n\t\t\t\tApr. 30 2026 01:00 PM EDT\n\t\t\t</span>\n</div>\n<h2 class=\"h4 u-margin-hug ceu-webinar-list__webinar__heading\">\n<a href=\"/ceu/webinars/backyards-and-beyond-what-todays-underwriters-really-see-20260430\">\n\t\t\t\tBackyards and Beyond:  What Today's Underwriters Really See\n\t\t\t</a>\n</h2>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__body\">\n<p>What do trampolines, TikTok, and AI have in common? They’re all shaping today’s underwriting decisions—see how far technology and lifestyle data really go. </p><ul><li>60 Minutes</li><li><span>Standard Webinar Price: $49.00</span></li><li><span>CEU Unlimited Subscriber Price: Included in your subscription.</span></li></ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__footer\">\n<a class=\"btn btn--secondary\" href=\"/ceu/webinars/backyards-and-beyond-what-todays-underwriters-really-see-20260430\">Learn More and Register<span class=\"u-sr-only\">for\n\t\t\t\t\tBackyards and Beyond:  What Today's Underwriters Really See</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div>\n<div class=\"views-row\">\n<article class=\"u-margin-lg-bottom u-box-shadow ceu-webinar-list__webinar\">\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__image\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2026-04/life-insurance-families-webinar-600x450.png%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__content\">\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__eyebrow\">\n<span class=\"u-text-uppercase badge badge--dark ceu-webinar-list__webinar__eyebrow__badge\">\n\t\t\t\tMay. 05 2026 11:00 AM EDT\n\t\t\t</span>\n</div>\n<h2 class=\"h4 u-margin-hug ceu-webinar-list__webinar__heading\">\n<a href=\"/ceu/webinars/stress-savings-and-stability-reframing-life-insurance-todays-families-20260505\">\n\t\t\t\tStress, Savings and Stability: Reframing Life Insurance for Today's Families\n\t\t\t</a>\n</h2>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__body\">\n<p>Discover how smart life insurance strategies can reduce stress, safeguard savings, and strengthen stability for families balancing the needs of multiple generations. </p><ul><li>60 Minutes</li><li><span>Standard Webinar Price: $49.00</span></li><li><span>CEU Unlimited Subscriber Price: Included in your subscription.</span></li></ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__footer\">\n<a class=\"btn btn--secondary\" href=\"/ceu/webinars/stress-savings-and-stability-reframing-life-insurance-todays-families-20260505\">Learn More and Register<span class=\"u-sr-only\">for\n\t\t\t\t\tStress, Savings and Stability: Reframing Life Insurance for Today's Families</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div>\n<div class=\"views-row\">\n<article class=\"u-margin-lg-bottom u-box-shadow ceu-webinar-list__webinar\">\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__image\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2026-03/webinar-cond-hoa-400x600.png%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__content\">\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__eyebrow\">\n<span class=\"u-text-uppercase badge badge--dark ceu-webinar-list__webinar__eyebrow__badge\">\n\t\t\t\tMay. 05 2026 01:00 PM EDT\n\t\t\t</span>\n</div>\n<h2 class=\"h4 u-margin-hug ceu-webinar-list__webinar__heading\">\n<a href=\"/ceu/webinars/bylaws-buildings-and-blind-spots-condo-and-hoa-coverage-explained-20260505\">\n\t\t\t\tBylaws, Buildings, and Blind Spots: Condo and HOA Coverage Explained\n\t\t\t</a>\n</h2>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__body\">\n<p>Clarify who insures what in condos and HOAs and spot the coverage gaps that create costly surprises when claims hit. </p><ul><li>120 Minutes</li><li><span>Standard Webinar Price: $64.00</span></li><li><span>CEU Unlimited Subscriber Price: Included in your subscription.</span></li></ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__footer\">\n<a class=\"btn btn--secondary\" href=\"/ceu/webinars/bylaws-buildings-and-blind-spots-condo-and-hoa-coverage-explained-20260505\">Learn More and Register<span class=\"u-sr-only\">for\n\t\t\t\t\tBylaws, Buildings, and Blind Spots: Condo and HOA Coverage Explained</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div>\n<div class=\"views-row\">\n<article class=\"u-margin-lg-bottom u-box-shadow ceu-webinar-list__webinar\">\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__image\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2026-02/webinar-justice-in-action-400x267.webp%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__content\">\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__eyebrow\">\n<span class=\"u-text-uppercase badge badge--dark ceu-webinar-list__webinar__eyebrow__badge\">\n\t\t\t\tMay. 06 2026 10:00 AM EDT\n\t\t\t</span>\n</div>\n<h2 class=\"h4 u-margin-hug ceu-webinar-list__webinar__heading\">\n<a href=\"/ceu/webinars/justice-action-how-insurance-fraud-reports-lead-real-prosecutions-20260506\">\n\t\t\t\tJustice in Action: How Insurance Fraud Reports Lead to Real Prosecutions\n\t\t\t</a>\n</h2>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__body\">\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">Discover how everyday fraud tips can lead to courtroom convictions. Real cases, sharp insights, and practical tools to help you recognize and report fraud with confidence.</span><span> </span></p><ul><li>120 Minutes</li><li><span>Standard Webinar Price: $64.00</span></li><li><span>CEU Unlimited Subscriber Price: Included in your subscription.</span></li></ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ceu-webinar-list__webinar__footer\">\n<a class=\"btn btn--secondary\" href=\"/ceu/webinars/justice-action-how-insurance-fraud-reports-lead-real-prosecutions-20260506\">Learn More and Register<span class=\"u-sr-only\">for\n\t\t\t\t\tJustice in Action: How Insurance Fraud Reports Lead to Real Prosecutions</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><p><strong>Important Note:</strong> <br/>Before retaking a course or webinar for CE credit, please confirm with your state licensing authority that repeat courses or webinars are eligible for credit in your renewal cycle. CE requirements vary by state and may not allow duplicate credit.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<section>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width\">\n<article class=\"container__grid media-block__container info-section info-section--background-white info-section--dropshadow info-section--img-left\">\n<div class=\"media-block__img-container\">\n<img alt=\"A young Asian woman works on a laptop while sitting on a couch in a living room.\" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/webp/public/2023-03/Woman_working_couch.jpg.webp?itok=ua4jlu4R\" srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/webp/public/2023-03/Woman_working_couch.jpg.webp?itok=ua4jlu4R 1x, /sites/default/files/styles/webp/public/2023-03/Woman_working_couch.jpg.webp?itok=ua4jlu4R  2x\"/>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"media-block__text\">\n<div class=\"media-block__header\">\n<span class=\"h5\"></span>\n<h2 class=\"u-margin-hug\">Stay Up to Date on CEU Webinars</h2>\n<hr aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"hr hr--offset hr--md hr--md--offset hr--light\" role=\"presentation\"/>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"media-block__content\">\n<p>We have big plans and many webinars in development. Stay updated on future CEU Webinars, share your email address below and watch your email for the latest updates in our webinars.</p><p>Sign up below to be one of the first to learn about exciting updates to CEU webinars!</p><p> </p><div class=\"_form_17 active_campaign_form\"> </div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</article>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n</div>\n<div>\n<section>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width\">\n<article class=\"container__grid media-block__container media-block__container--reversed\">\n<div class=\"media-block__img-container\">\n<img alt=\"A happy piggy bank sits on a pile of money. \" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/right_aligned/public/2023-02/piggy_bank-on_money.png?itok=Mn4S5ZjA\" srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/right_aligned/public/2023-02/piggy_bank-on_money.png?itok=Mn4S5ZjA 1x, /sites/default/files/styles/right_aligned_2x/public/2023-02/piggy_bank-on_money.png?itok=YjMgK5wf  2x\"/>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"media-block__header\">\n<h2 class=\"u-margin-hug\">\n            Enjoy unlimited access to webinars with CEU Unlimited.\n          </h2>\n<hr aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"hr hr--offset hr--md hr--md--offset hr--light\" role=\"presentation\"/>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"media-block__content\">\n<p>As a new or current CEU Unlimited Subscriber, enjoy 12 months of full access to every CEU Webinar. That is in addition to 12 months unlimited access to our robust library of on-demand courses.</p><p>PLUS, there are NO state reporting and NO hidden fees for our webinars and on-demand courses– the price you see is the price you pay, period.</p><p>Get your CEU Unlimited today.</p><p><em>*CEU Unlimited subscriber webinar discount will be reflected in the checkout process. <span style=\"color:#7F132A;\"><strong>No discount code or pre-paid agreement number required!</strong></span></em></p>\n<div class=\"card__btn-container card__btn-container--single\" data-item-id=\"31943\" data-learn-more-external=\"\" data-learn-more-text=\"\" data-learn-more-url=\"\" data-price=\"85.00\" data-product=\"CEU Unlimited Access Program\" data-react-component-id=\"add-to-cart\">\n<button class=\"btn btn--primary btn--disabled\">Add to Cart - &amp;dollar;</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</article>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div></body></html>",
